summary.text:
```json
{
  type: "array",
  options: {
    syncEnum: {
      source: "#/pointer/to/string-list"
    }
  },
  items: {
    type: "string",
    enum: []
  }
}
```

 with a json-pointer from root to target-value.

e.g. { setOptionTitleTo: "#/main/menu/title" }

Json-schema usage when adding this plugin:

```
 selection: {
   type: "string",
   enum: [1, 2, 3],
   options: {
     enum: ["One Title", "Two Title", "Three title"]
   },
   setOptionTitleTo: "#/title"
 },
 title: {
   type: "string",
   options: { disabled: true }
 }
```
